                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I saw him take it out of the pocket—he</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183505110206"></xptr>
               <p>begged me to let him go, and said, it was his first offence, and that he would go away from the fair.</p>
               <p>(Thomas Drew, in whose employ the prisoner had been, gave him a good character, and offered to take him into his service.)</p>
